    <string name="onboarding_title_3">Keep NotiFetch Alive</string>
    <string name="onboarding_desc_3">Android may kill NotiFetch in the background to save battery, stopping notification capture. Tap below to whitelist NotiFetch from battery optimization.\n\nOn Xiaomi/Samsung/OPPO/Vivo, you may also need to enable \'Auto-start\' in OEM-specific settings.</string>
